### 二手交易平台API测试文件
### 测试环境配置：http-client.env.json

## 1. 用户注册接口测试

### 1.1 正常注册测试
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser0001",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户1",
  "phone": "13912355678"
}

### 1.2 注册失败 - 用户名已存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456",
  "nickname": "重复用户",
  "phone": "13987654321"
}

### 1.3 注册失败 - 密码不一致
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser002",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "654321",
  "nickname": "密码错误测试",
  "phone": "13712345678"
}

### 1.4 注册失败 - 用户名格式不正确
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test-user",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456",
  "nickname": "格式错误测试",
  "phone": "13612345678"
}

### 1.5 注册失败 - 手机号格式不正确
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser003",
  "password": "123456",
  "confirmPassword": "123456",
  "nickname": "手机格式错误",
  "phone": "12345678901"
}

### 2. 用户登录接口测试

### 2.1 正常登录测试
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2.2 登录失败 - 用户不存在
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nonexistent",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 2.3 登录失败 - 密码错误
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 2.4 登录失败 - 参数缺失
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin"
}

### 3. 用户状态检查接口测试

### 3.1 检查登录状态（未登录）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/check-login

### 3.2 获取用户信息（未登录）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/info

## 4. 登录后功能测试

### 4.1 用户登录获取token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4.2 提取登录token用于后续请求
@authToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.token}}

### 4.3 检查登录状态（已登录）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/check-login
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 4.4 获取用户信息（已登录）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/info
Authorization: {{authToken}}

## 5. 用户登出测试

### 5.1 用户登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: {{authToken}}

### 5.2 登出后检查登录状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/check-login

### 5.3 登出后尝试获取用户信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/info
Authorization: {{authToken}}